{
  "video_id": "qKJv4S5peJQ",
  "title": "What happens in your brain when you pay attention? | Mehdi Ordikhani-Seyedlar",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 15600.0,
      "text": "Paying close attention to something:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15100.0,
      "end_time": 16340.0,
      "text": "Not that easy, is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17340.0,
      "end_time": 22356.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because our attention is pulled in so many different directions at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22380.0,
      "end_time": 26460.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s in fact pretty impressive if you can stay focused."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28180.0,
      "end_time": 32235.0,
      "text": "Many people think that attention is all about what we are focusing on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 37590.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s also about what information our brain is trying to filter out."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38140.0,
      "end_time": 40860.0,
      "text": "There are two ways you direct your attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 41420.0,
      "end_time": 42980.0,
      "text": "First, there&#39;s overt attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43460.0,
      "end_time": 47596.0,
      "text": "In overt attention, you move your eyes towards something"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47620.0,
      "end_time": 49180.0,
      "text": "in order to pay attention to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50180.0,
      "end_time": 52156.0,
      "text": "Then there&#39;s covert attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52180.0,
      "end_time": 56196.0,
      "text": "In covert attention, you pay attention to something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 56220.0,
      "end_time": 57780.0,
      "text": "but without moving your eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58860.0,
      "end_time": 60500.0,
      "text": "Think of driving for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62780.0,
      "end_time": 65796.0,
      "text": "Your overt attention, your direction of the eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65820.0,
      "end_time": 67476.0,
      "text": "are in front,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67500.0,
      "end_time": 69276.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s your covert attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69300.0,
      "end_time": 72380.0,
      "text": "which is constantly scanning the surrounding area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73420.0,
      "end_time": 75300.0,
      "text": "where you don&#39;t actually look at them."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77339.0,
      "end_time": 79276.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a computational neuroscientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79300.0,
      "end_time": 82396.0,
      "text": "and I work on cognitive brain-machine interfaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82420.0,
      "end_time": 85460.0,
      "text": "or bringing together the brain and the computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86540.0,
      "end_time": 88140.0,
      "text": "I love brain patterns."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88540.0,
      "end_time": 90236.0,
      "text": "Brain patterns are important for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 93756.0,
      "text": "because based on them we can build models for the computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93780.0,
      "end_time": 95196.0,
      "text": "and based on these models"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95220.0,
      "end_time": 99436.0,
      "text": "computers can recognize how well our brain functions."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99460.0,
      "end_time": 101590.0,
      "text": "And if it doesn&#39;t function well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101900.0,
      "end_time": 105820.0,
      "text": "then these computers themselves can be used as assistive devices"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106580.0,
      "end_time": 107780.0,
      "text": "for therapies."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108300.0,
      "end_time": 109940.0,
      "text": "But that also means something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111180.0,
      "end_time": 113676.0,
      "text": "because choosing the wrong patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113700.0,
      "end_time": 115596.0,
      "text": "will give us the wrong models"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115620.0,
      "end_time": 117276.0,
      "text": "and therefore the wrong therapies."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117300.0,
      "end_time": 118500.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119460.0,
      "end_time": 121116.0,
      "text": "In case of attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121140.0,
      "end_time": 122420.0,
      "text": "the fact that we can"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123620.0,
      "end_time": 127116.0,
      "text": "shift our attention not only by our eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127140.0,
      "end_time": 128460.0,
      "text": "but also by thinking --"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133340.0,
      "text": "that makes covert attention an interesting model for computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134100.0,
      "end_time": 137555.0,
      "text": "So I wanted to know what are the brainwave patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137580.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "when you look overtly or when you look covertly."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144190.0,
      "text": "I set up an experiment for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144780.0,
      "end_time": 147516.0,
      "text": "In this experiment there are two flickering squares,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147540.0,
      "end_time": 150900.0,
      "text": "one of them flickering at a slower rate than the other one."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152420.0,
      "end_time": 156236.0,
      "text": "Depending on which of these flickers you are paying attention to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 160220.0,
      "text": "certain parts of your brain will start resonating in the same rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161200.0,
      "end_time": 162460.0,
      "text": "as that flickering rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163820.0,
      "end_time": 166756.0,
      "text": "So by analyzing your brain signals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166780.0,
      "end_time": 169820.0,
      "text": "we can track where exactly you are watching"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170580.0,
      "end_time": 172140.0,
      "text": "or you are paying attention to."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 174820.0,
      "end_time": 179360.0,
      "text": "So to see what happens in your brain when you pay overt attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 179600.0,
      "end_time": 182316.0,
      "text": "I asked people to look directly in one of the squares"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182340.0,
      "end_time": 183620.0,
      "text": "and pay attention to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 184580.0,
      "end_time": 189876.0,
      "text": "In this case, not surprisingly, we saw that these flickering squares"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189900.0,
      "end_time": 191836.0,
      "text": "appeared in their brain signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 191860.0,
      "end_time": 194220.0,
      "text": "which was coming from the back of their head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 195380.0,
      "end_time": 198780.0,
      "text": "which is responsible for the processing of your visual information."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200100.0,
      "end_time": 202436.0,
      "text": "But I was really interested"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 202460.0,
      "end_time": 205620.0,
      "text": "to see what happens in your brain when you pay covert attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 206300.0,
      "end_time": 210196.0,
      "text": "So this time I asked people to look in the middle of the screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 210220.0,
      "end_time": 212100.0,
      "text": "and without moving their eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212940.0,
      "end_time": 215660.0,
      "text": "to pay attention to either of these squares."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216940.0,
      "end_time": 218556.0,
      "text": "When we did that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 218580.0,
      "end_time": 222516.0,
      "text": "we saw that both of these flickering rates appeared in their brain signals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 222540.0,
      "end_time": 223739.0,
      "text": "but interestingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 224460.0,
      "end_time": 227996.0,
      "text": "only one of them, which was paid attention to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228200.0,
      "end_time": 229676.0,
      "text": "had stronger signals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 229700.0,
      "end_time": 231956.0,
      "text": "so there was something in the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 231980.0,
      "end_time": 234516.0,
      "text": "which was handling this information"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 234540.0,
      "end_time": 240739.0,
      "text": "so that thing in the brain was basically the activation of the frontal area."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245236.0,
      "text": "The front part of your brain is responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 248140.0,
      "text": "for higher cognitive functions as a human."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 248980.0,
      "end_time": 253420.0,
      "text": "The frontal part, it seems that it works as a filter"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 254460.0,
      "end_time": 258836.0,
      "text": "trying to let information come in only from the right flicker"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 258860.0,
      "end_time": 260500.0,
      "text": "that you are paying attention to"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261220.00000000003,
      "end_time": 265180.0,
      "text": "and trying to inhibit the information coming from the ignored one."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267220.0,
      "end_time": 272516.0,
      "text": "The filtering ability of the brain is indeed a key for attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 272540.0,
      "end_time": 275316.0,
      "text": "which is missing in some people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275340.0,
      "end_time": 277820.0,
      "text": "for example in people with ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 278460.0,
      "end_time": 283476.0,
      "text": "So a person with ADHD cannot inhibit these distractors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 283500.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why they can&#39;t focus for a long time on a single task."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 289420.0,
      "end_time": 290956.0,
      "text": "But what if this person"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 290980.0,
      "end_time": 294516.0,
      "text": "could play a specific computer game"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 294540.0,
      "end_time": 297420.0,
      "text": "with his brain connected to the computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300380.0,
      "text": "and then train his own brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 301180.0,
      "end_time": 303620.0,
      "text": "to inhibit these distractors?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 305500.0,
      "end_time": 307980.0,
      "text": "Well, ADHD is just one example."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 309200.0,
      "end_time": 312275.0,
      "text": "We can use these cognitive brain-machine interfaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 312300.0,
      "end_time": 314500.0,
      "text": "for many other cognitive fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 315580.0,
      "end_time": 317356.0,
      "text": "It was just a few years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 317380.0,
      "end_time": 323100.0,
      "text": "that my grandfather had a stroke, and he lost complete ability to speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 324460.0,
      "end_time": 327796.0,
      "text": "He could understand everybody, but there was no way to respond,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 327820.0,
      "end_time": 330300.0,
      "text": "even not writing because he was illiterate."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 331820.0,
      "end_time": 334340.0,
      "text": "So he passed away in silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 336620.0,
      "end_time": 338956.0,
      "text": "I remember thinking at that time:"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 338980.0,
      "end_time": 342876.0,
      "text": "What if we could have a computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 342900.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "which could speak for him?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 345660.0,
      "end_time": 347876.0,
      "text": "Now, after years that I am in this field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 347900.0,
      "end_time": 350219.0,
      "text": "I can see that this might be possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 352600.0,
      "end_time": 354916.0,
      "text": "Imagine if we can find brainwave patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 354940.0,
      "end_time": 358380.0,
      "text": "when people think about images or even letters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 359540.0,
      "end_time": 362476.0,
      "text": "like the letter A generates a different brainwave pattern"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 362500.0,
      "end_time": 364220.0,
      "text": "than the letter B, and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 364780.0,
      "end_time": 368460.0,
      "text": "Could a computer one day communicate for people who can&#39;t speak?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 369460.0,
      "end_time": 370900.0,
      "text": "What if a computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 371780.0,
      "end_time": 376340.0,
      "text": "can help us understand the thoughts of a person in a coma?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 377660.0,
      "end_time": 379276.0,
      "text": "We are not there yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 379300.0,
      "end_time": 382360.0,
      "text": "but pay close attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 382600.0,
      "end_time": 383756.0,
      "text": "We will be there soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 383780.0,
      "end_time": 385275.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 385300.0,
      "end_time": 390932.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}